message.body: O wut up cashewlover85! How you been?
Haha! I've been ok, sorry I never got a chance to text back the other night
How are you?
Its alright. I'm doing pretty well, went for a run last night and I am sore as all get out today
That's cool, not fun being sore though. I've been doing these calf raises at the gym ... Brutal!
O yea? Trying to be one of those massive calves people? I've been trying pose running. Also brutal on the calves
No,def don't want bigger calves. Trying to tone/get smaller in general.
What's pose running?
Its where you strike with your forefoot instead of your heel first. Supposed to be more natural
Ah, I've heard of that. Sounds kinda hard though, to change the way you run ... Don't really know tho, not a runner myself
Yea I mean its basically slow motion sprinting, but it makes sense after your legs get used to it. Man today has been packed with meetings!
Ugh yeah, I hate meetings sometimes
Glad the work day is over
Are you in NYC today?
Yup! I mean my work day goes a little later but it is coming to a close
I miss going to ny, it's been a while
Do you gave time to go out or just work when u r there?
I have time to go out some. I'm meeting up with some family in the area for dinner tonight actually
Nice, where are you going?
... Waiting for the subway, ridiculously long today
Idk. Somewhere in financial district. Which city are you in?
Philadelphia
The subway here sucks, you can only go 2 ways
Yea I was in Philly for a bit the other month but never rode it. I think everyone hates their commute
True. At the park with my dog now best part of the day
Heck that's great! What kinda dog?
She's a mut, black lab and some unknowns. She looks like a tall, skinny black lab with longish fur
I had a black lab mut growing up. Shorter hair though. Is yours anxious? Mine had real bad separation anxiety
She's fine being left in the normal routine, work day and stuff but if you start packing for a trip,she gets nervous
Haha its funny how they know things like that
